<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:36:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队指挥官允许定居者对希伯伦族长墓进行翻修，并向上级隐瞒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-commander-allows-settlers-to-do-renovation-at-tomb-of-the-patriarchs-of-his-own-accord/00000191-0f56-d3d4-adb1-3fdf80b50000</link><description>伊谢·罗西利奥上校因越权并在未通知上级的情况下允许在族长墓的屋顶上工作而受到谴责。族长墓是犹太教和伊斯兰教的圣地，一直是犹太人和穆斯林之间的冲突点</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-commander-allows-settlers-to-do-renovation-at-tomb-of-the-patriarchs-of-his-own-accord/00000191-0f56-d3d4-adb1-3fdf80b50000</guid></item><item><title>真主党纳斯鲁拉承诺对高级指挥官被杀作出回应，称战争进入“新阶段”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/hezbollahs-nasrallah-promises-response-to-killing-of-senior-commander/00000191-0f53-dc54-a7dd-ffd3a3bb0000</link><description>纳斯鲁拉再次否认真主党参与了上周对迈季代勒沙姆斯发动的火箭弹袭击，造成12名儿童和青少年死亡，并呼吁世界各国向以色列施压，要求其停止加沙战争</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 19:30:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/hezbollahs-nasrallah-promises-response-to-killing-of-senior-commander/00000191-0f53-dc54-a7dd-ffd3a3bb0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日以来 300 天，数千名以色列人呼吁内塔尼亚胡签署人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/thousands-attend-tel-aviv-rally-as-israel-marks-300-days-since-october-7/00000191-0ef3-d782-af93-1ffb554d0000</link><description>“我已经300天没有拥抱过父亲了。距离我看到他穿着内衣被带离家已经过去 300 天了。距离我上次和他说话已经过去 300 天了。请把我的父亲带回到我身边，”埃拉·本·阿米说道，她的父亲被哈马斯关押在加沙地带</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid is