好准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-amid-fears-that-intel-will-announce-job-cuts/00000191-0d77-dbed-a5f9-dff7ed920000</link><description>随着这家美国芯片巨头建造更多工厂，它必须在其他地方削减开支。以色列人还将寻找英特尔是否真的停止在以色列建设新工厂的线索</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:19:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-amid-fears-that-intel-will-announce-job-cuts/00000191-0d77-dbed-a5f9-dff7ed920000</guid></item><item><title>以色列研究表明智能手表可以警告您患有新冠病毒或即将发生偏头痛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-study-shows-smartwatches-can-warn-you-have-covid-or-a-migraine-is-about-to-happen/00000191-0e9d-d4cf-afb5-4edd06130000</link><description>特殊的传感器使特拉维夫大学的科学家能够在患者出现症状之前识别出新冠病毒、流感和链球菌性咽喉炎的迹象。下一个目标：偏头痛和高血糖</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-study-shows-smartwatches-can-warn-you-have-covid-or-a-migraine-is-about-to-happen/00000191-0e9d-d4cf-afb5-4edd06130000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列能杀死伊朗的哈尼亚，肯定能把115人从加沙带回国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-01/ty-article/.highlight/if-israel-can-kill-haniyeh-in-iran-it-can-surely-bring-115-people-back-home-from-gaza/00000191-0eea-dc54-a7dd-ffeaf9260000</link><description>已经300天了，我不知道那些关键人物，那些谈论彻底胜利的人，有没有哭过。我不确定他们是否意识到每个人质的名字都蕴藏着灵魂</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:11:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-01/ty-article/.highlight/if-israel-can-kill-haniyeh-in-iran-it-can-surely-bring-115-people-back-home-from-gaza/00000191-0eea-dc54-a7dd-ffeaf9260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 300 天：以色列呼吁公民在国外谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-300-israel-calls-on-citizens-to-exercise-caution-abroad/00000191-0ed4-d782-af93-1fdc9f490001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列已做好应对任何情况的准备，并将与美国总统拜登进行对话 ■ 西方外交官警告称，贝鲁特和德黑兰发生暗杀事件后，战争风险有所增加 ■ 真主党领袖纳斯鲁拉：“我们在所有领域都进入了一个新阶段” ■ 以色列证实，哈马斯军事首领穆罕默德·德伊夫 (Mohammed Deif) 在 7 月以色列国防军对汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 的袭击中丧生 ■ 以下是战争 300 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 16:51:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-300-israel-calls-on-citizens-to-exercise-caution-abroad/00000191-0ed4-d782-af93-1fdc9f490001</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》报道称，哈马斯领导人哈尼亚被德黑兰宾馆安置的炸弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-haniyeh-killed-by-bomb-planted-in-tehran-guesthouse-nyt-report-says/00000191-0e65-d782-af93-1ffd4fcc0000</link><description>该报告与早前关于这位政治领袖在一次有针对性的空袭中丧生的猜测相矛盾。伊朗官员称这次暗杀是伊朗情报和安全方面的灾难性失败，也是革命卫队的重大尴尬</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-haniyeh-killed-by-bomb-planted-in-tehran-guesthouse-nyt-report-says/00000191-0e65-d782-af93-1ffd4fcc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列是否故意挑起冲突升级，从而可能将美国拖入冲突？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/is-israel-deliberately-provoking-escalation-that-might-drag-the-u-s-into-the-conflict/00000191-0e5d-dc54-a7dd-ffdfbb610000</link><description>本周在贝鲁特和德黑兰发生的定点杀戮引发了三个基本问题，其中最大的一个是：谁在扩大的地区战争中拥有既得利益？</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/is-israel-deliberately-provoking-escalation-that-might-drag-the-u-s-into-the-conflict/00000191-0e5d-dc54-a7dd-ffdfbb610000</guid></item><item><title>“世俗的人以更复杂的方式应对生活。宗教提供了解决方案，但它们并不真实”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-01/ty-article/.highlight/secular-people-cope-with-life-in-a-far-more-complex-way/00000191-0e84-dc54-a7dd-ffc6ddc70000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名以色列人在抛开宗教信仰后开始潜水，而一名美国数字游牧者开始想家</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-01/ty-article/.highlight/secular-people-cope-with-life-in-a-far-more-complex-way/00000191-0e84-dc54-a7dd-ffc6ddc70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列柔道运动员因巴尔·拉尼尔和彼得·帕尔奇克夺得银牌和铜牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-clinches-its-first-medal-in-2024-olympics/00000191-0e79-d4cf-afb5-4efd11bb0000</link><description>因巴尔·拉尼尔（Inbal Lanir）在女子78公斤级柔道比赛中获得银牌，帕尔奇克（Paltchik）击败瑞士选手丹尼尔·艾希（Daniel Eich）获得铜牌</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-clinches-its-first-medal-in-2024-olympics/00000191-0e79-d4cf-afb5-4efd11bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长正在考虑对闯入斯德·泰曼基地的 MK 提起诉讼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-mulls-possible-indictments-against-mks-who-broke-into-sde-teiman-base/00000191-0d95-d116-a5d9-0ffdaaa30000</link><description>工党议员 Efrat Reiten 在向总检察长提出的上诉中表示，Zvi Succot 和 Nissim Vaturi 未经授权进入军事基地是严重犯罪行为，不属于议会豁免权范围。法律专家解释原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 13:44:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-mulls-possible-indictments-against-mks-who-broke-into-sde-teiman-base/00000191-0d95-d116-a5d9-0ffdaaa30000</guid></item><item><title>愤怒、震惊和怀疑：阿拉伯世界对哈尼亚在德黑兰遇刺事件的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/anger-shock-and-suspicion-arab-world-reacts-to-haniyehs-assassination-in-tehran/00000191-0d6a-dc54-a7dd-ffea7b970000</link><description>虽然一名伊朗记者称伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚 (Ismail Haniyeh) 被杀比 2020 年卡西姆·苏莱马尼 (Qassem Soleimani) 将军的死更为严重，但一些人将指责的矛头指向伊斯兰共和国和以色列</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 13:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/anger-shock-and-suspicion-arab-world-reacts-to-haniyehs-assassination-in-tehran/00000191-0d6a-dc54-a7dd-ffea7b970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列证实，哈马斯军事首领、10 月 7 日建筑师穆罕默德·德伊夫 (Mohammed Deif) 在上个月加沙袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-confirms-it-killed-hamas-military-chief-mohammed-deif-in-gaza-strike-in-july/00000191-0d33-dba6-a59d-0f7ba0d40000</link><description>以色列国防军和辛贝特的一份联合声明称，德伊夫在上个月对汗尤尼斯大院的一次袭击中身亡，并杀死了其他哈马斯成员。加沙医疗消息人士称，另有约 90 人在袭击中丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 12:22:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-confirms-it-killed-hamas-military-chief-mohammed-deif-in-gaza-strike-in-july/00000191-0d33-dba6-a59d-0f7ba0d40000</guid></item><item><title>由于安全局势，汉莎航空取消 8 月 8 日之前飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/lufthansa-cancels-flights-to-israel-until-august-8-due-to-security-situation/00000191-0db5-dc1a-a3dd-2dffe8750000</link><description>周三，搭乘慕尼黑-特拉维夫经拉纳卡航班的乘客因转机航班取消，不得不留在塞浦路斯等待返回以色列的航班；汉莎航空飞往贝鲁特的航班取消至 8 月 12 日</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 11:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/lufthansa-cancels-flights-to-israel-until-august-8-due-to-security-situation/00000191-0db5-dc1a-a3dd-2dffe8750000</guid></item><item><title>实时假新闻：以色列 Telegram 频道如何接管新闻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fake-news-in-real-time-how-israeli-telegram-channels-took-over-the-news/00000191-090f-d4cf-afb5-4ddfc89c0000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，在线团体比电视新闻更快，比报纸影响力更大，在以色列已经获得了数十万追随者</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:34:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fake-news-in-real-time-how-israeli-telegram-channels-took-over-the-news/00000191-090f-d4cf-afb5-4ddfc89c0000</guid></item><item><title>“国际机构对以色列的压力产生了影响。高等法院法官现在听我们的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/pressure-from-international-bodies-has-an-effect-high-court-judges-listen-to-us-now/00000191-09bc-daf5-a7db-effccfae0000</link><description>二十一个以色列非政府组织最近发布了第二份“占领状况”报告——这份令人痛心的报告将加沙战争、西岸定居者暴力以及以色列公民自由的恶化联系在一起。人权医生组织的盖伊·沙莱夫表示，报告中的哈马斯大屠杀不应该被用来压制对以色列暴行的批评</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:46:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/pressure-from-international-bodies-has-an-effect-high-court-judges-listen-to-us-now/00000191-09bc-daf5-a7db-effccfae0000</guid></item></channel></rss>